author: gordonsmith
msg: Falcon unit tests: Added more parsing tests for <Number> tags and properties of type Number, to check whether we can handle hex integers, scientific notation, NaN, and positive negative Infinity.
This revealed a bug: If p is a property of type Number, <MyComp p="1"/> currently produces an MXMLIntTag to represent the value. It should produce a MXMLNumberTag.
